textAnnotations.description:
DIRECTIONS FOR OPERATING
BEFORE USING- SEE THAT BOWL
FLAPPER VALVE "A IS CLOSED. GATE VALVE
"CIN DISCHARGE PIPE LINE IS OPEN.
VALVE OIN WATER SSUPPLY LINE IS OPEN.
THEN OPEN VALVE E NEXT TO BOWL
TO ADMIT NECESSARY WATER. CLOSE
VALVES "D AND 'E.
AFTER USING
PULL LEVER A. RELEASE LEVER A".
FOR AIR EXPULSION
ROCK AIR VALVE "P LEVER OUTBOARD
TO CHARGE MEASURING TANK 10 LBS
ABOVE SEA PRESSURE OPEN VALVE B
AND ROCK AIR VALVE LEVER INBOARD TO
BLOW OVERBOARD, CLOSE VALVE .
CLOSE VALVE C.
FOR PUMP EXPULSION
OPEN VALVE 8" PUMP WASTE RECEVER
EMPTY CLOSE VALVE . CLOSE VALVE
